ixtures. While scrambling to move everything off the counter, my roommate managed to call the front desk to report this disaster. Turned out the guest upstairs had left the tub running when he left the room, overflowing onto the floors, and into our room below.... We got moved up to a larger room, thankfully. Last event: A mouse ran across the lobby floor in front of us as we went toward the elevator late at night, headed up for our room. No one screamed. I think the night manager was happy to see us leave. It's hard when a guest has those many things happen on consecutive nights... 
